Buffett didn't make most of his wealth until he was well into his 30s. But Buffett was never in this for the money...he wanted the independence. He made it BIG from long term investing alone, and anyone can do that.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Business Instantly on August 11, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'Bastiaan Slot @_bastiaanslot 7 principles that made me a millionaire in my early 20s. (A thread)'.

Photo by Business Instantly on August 11, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and text that says 'Bastiaan Slot @_bastiaanslot Goal setting. If you don't know what you want, then you don't know what to do. Set one clear, tangible goal. Achieve your goal, then repeat.'.

Photo by Business Instantly on August 11, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and text that says 'Bastiaan Slot @_bastiaanslot 2. Sacrifice. If you don't sacrifice for what you want, then your goal becomes the sacrifice.'.

Photo by Business Instantly on August 11, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'Bastiaan Slot @_bastiaanslot 3. Health. Sleep wel Eat healthy. Meditate. Exercise. Take time to relax. If you aren't performing at your best, your business won't either.'.

Photo by Business Instantly on August 11, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and text that says 'Bastiaan Slot @_bastiaanslot 4. Gratitude. Always looking to the future future can cause fear, anxiety, and stress. Practice gratitude daily to balance yourself.'.

Photo by Business Instantly on August 11, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'Bastiaan Slot @_bastiaanslot 5. Resist impulses. When you're working, resist all urges to eat snacks, grab a treat, or check social media. Train yourself to stay focused on the task at hand, and don't let anything distract you that's how you make progress.'.

Photo by Business Instantly on August 11, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and text that says 'Bastiaan Slot @_bastiaanslot 6. Consistency. Whether you're seeing great results or no results at all, you need to stay consistent. Stay consistent without expecting immediate results. It will all add up long term.'.

Photo by Business Instantly on August 11, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'Bastiaan Slot @_bastiaanslot 7. Invest in yourself. etc. Whether it's books, mentors, seminars, Make sure you're constantly investing in your own growth. You don't have to figure out everything on your own. Find someone who has the results you want and learn from them. That's your "shortcut" to success.'.

Photo by Business Instantly on August 11, 2021. May be an image of one or more people and text that says 'Bastiaan Slot @_bastiaanslot Whenever you're feeling stuck or like you're not making progress in life life you can always go back to these principles and see where you're going wrong. |focus on these daily to make sure I stay on track'.

Photo by Business Instantly on August 11, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'Bastiaan Slot @_bastiaanslot If you'd like to see more content and tips abon what learned from building a 7-figure consulting business, drop me a follow.'.
